HEADWORD: Insistence
<hw>In*sist"ence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of
insisting, or being urgent or pressing; the act of dwelling upon as of
special importance; persistence; urgency.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

